<https://www.uncorkedstudios.com/blog/uncorked-new-office-811-stark/|Uncorked's New Home: 811 Stark>
At Uncorked we build things every day. It’s the common bond between all team members.

But when so much of what we build exists as code, or in production runs where it’s relatively straightforward to make changes, the big things deserve special mention.

On May 1, 2017 we launched something on an entirely new scale for Uncorked, something for us that’s truly monumental. We’re pleased to dedicate 811 Stark as our new home in Portland’s Central Eastside.

In a radical, no-going-back...

attachments.title: Uncorked's New Home: 811 Stark
attachments.text: At Uncorked we build things every day. It’s the common bond between all team members. But when so much of what we build exists as code, or in production runs where it’s relatively straightforward to make changes, the big things deserve special mention. On May 1, 2017 we launched something on an entirely new scale for Uncorked, something for us that’s truly monumental. We’re pleased to dedicate 811 Stark as our new home in Portland’s Central Eastside.
